  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个用户旅程图，记录我典型的工作日流程。整体分成两大块：上班去和回家。标题就叫'My working day'吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey",
        "title My working day",
        "section Go to work",
        "section Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个section分别是'Go to work'和'Go home'。每个环节需要标注满意度分数和参与者对吧？您先说说上班这段有哪些步骤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go to work",
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，上班路上我先泡茶，这个体验不错，给5分，只有我自己。然后上楼去工作区，稍微麻烦点，3分。最后实际干活最痛苦，1分，而且我家猫会来捣乱，所以参与者要加上Cat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea: 5: Me",
        "Go upstairs: 3: Me",
        "Do work: 1: Me, Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，上班部分：泡茶5分、上楼3分、干活1分（Me和Cat）。那回家这段呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go to work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "回家就轻松多了。先下楼，5分，然后坐下来休息，也是5分。这两个都是我自己完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs: 5: Me",
        "Sit down: 5: Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，您看一下。上班部分三个环节，回家部分两个环节，分数和参与者都按您说的标了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey",
        "title My working day",
        "section Go to work",
        "section Go home",
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work",
        "Go downstairs",
        "Sit down"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，'Go home'这个section标题是不是拼错了？我刚才口误说的，应该是'Go home'不是'Go wnstairs'那种奇怪的东西。哦不对，我是说section名，你写的是对的。但我再看一眼——不对，'Go home'没问题，但上楼那个环节，我刚才说的是'Go upstairs'，你确认下拼写？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go upstairs"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查过了，'Go upstairs'拼写正确，两个section标题也都对的。整个图结构是：标题My working day，两个section分别是Go to work和Go home，五个环节分数和参与者都准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title My working day",
